npm init 
npm i -D typescript
npx tsc --init
npx tsc   //Compaile typescript to javascript

Note:
1.Typescript give you compaile time error and js give you run time errro.
2. Typescript is only use in the development but when the code gets compaile for production all the type information will removed.

Lint
npm install --save-dev @typescript-eslint/parser @typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin eslint 
npx eslint .
npm install --save-dev eslint-config-prettier
npm run lint